-- [Config] ‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏™‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏õ‡∏ï‡πå‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏î‡∏±‡∏ö
local VIP_SCRIPT_URL = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/stampx85-byte/Humanx1/refs/heads/main/kill%20Aura%20all"
